        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="572,0,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="The diagram below shows the basic components of a typical microcontroller design where the vendor uses ARM Cortex M Processors as their choice of CPU. uController vendors for ARM Cortex Processors e.g vendors include ADI, Atmel, TI and Microsemi. The processors are also used on SoCs for audio processing and power management systems. Also utilized in mixed signal designs since analog ICs such as PMIC and MEMS, sensors also include processors." VerticalAlignment="Top" Height="204" Width="454" Background="{DynamicResource {x:Static SystemColors.ControlLightLightBrushKey}}" FontSize="14"/>
